description_of_request:
This is a request under the Illinois Freedom of Information Act (5 ILCS 140). Please provide me with the following records:
• An Excel spreadsheet listing all of the agencies that applied through 2 RFP rounds for early learning funding through the City of Chicago Department of Family Services, with the column headings for agency name, site address, number of seats in the 2019 application, and scores on RFP rounds 1 and 2 (whichever is applicable); 
• An Excel spreadsheet listing how much funding was awarded per site through the combined RFPs 1 and 2 and for how many seats; 
• An Excel spreadsheet of grantees from the last funding round 2015 whose program funding was eliminated.
